{"type": "article", "id": 27498, "title": "防盗智能自行车", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-30T07:04:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 40, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702142455Vr4u2wHxMhaSn8DX.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>老丢自行车的朋友们，这辆由阿姆斯特丹自行车公司 VanMoof 推出的 SmartBike 或许是你的福音。这款自行车的上管前端配备了 GSM 和蓝牙追踪系统，被盗后 VanMoof 的团队会为车主定位自行车的位置。VanMoof 还提供了一个在购买后的前两年完全免费的服务：如果在失窃后的两周内没有办法物归原主，VanMoof 会为车主替换一辆新的自行车。SmartBike 还是一辆无锁的自行车，车主可以通过配套的手机应用或者是把手放在上管上解锁自行车。如果你对这个智能的自行车感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"https://www.vanmoof.com/en_us/bikes/smart-straight\">链接</a>订购，售价为 1098 美元起。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142453slWrOISxtj6FC5iR.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142454uDaFlSMUf28J4okr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6992665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142454GjwKRBX2lm8Sz6Ey.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6992665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142455HJwRjP63oishWrqy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}